title: askybiock空岛插件打/is出现了这个玩意
author: Lucency
txt_content:
More set up is required before the plugin can start...
更多的设置是必需的，在插件可以开始…
The world generator for the island world is not registered.
世界上没有注册的世界发电机。
Potential reasons are：
潜在原因：
1.If you are configuring the world as the only server world
1、如果您正在配置世界作为唯一的服务器世界
Make sure you have added the world to bukkit.yml
确保你加入世界bukkit.yml
2.You reloaded instead of restarting the server. Reboot and try again.
2。你重装上阵而不是重新启动服务器。重新启动并重试。
3.Your Multiverse plugin is out of date. Upgrade to the latest version.
3。你的多元宇宙的插件是过时的。升级到最新版本。




鸡翻

最后的30多金粒表嫌少
